{
  "stem": "11964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I did not know-- after the very moment that I left the Warsaw ghetto, I did not know-- I did not get any information.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because, obviously, the German newspapers were only hailing the German victories.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As a Pole, I could read a German newspaper, the official German newspaper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But all you read there is about their victories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I, I really do not recall the knowledge of any of the gas chambers, or the ovens, or, or, or the death camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This wasn't a factory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in an office.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I, I don't think that the Poles themselves would have discussed anything in the earshot-- within the earshot of German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the German were-- the, the Germans were their enemies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they abhorred them greatly, with the exception of some of the people-- so-called 'Volksdeutsche.' Volksdeutsche were people-- Poles-- who were of German origin.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because they were of German origin, when the Germans came, they knew that they could, number one, serve the Germans; number two, receive very preferential treatment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So these Volksdeutsche were very, very helpful to the Germans in discovering those Poles who were anti-Nazi and, of course, Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the conversation among the Poles was very private.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they abhorred the, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they hated them just as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--we, we went-- we, we, we decided to take the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- what we later found out-- was the last train leaving Warsaw, when we got to Busko.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "While we came to Busko, I realized that it was an altogether different place from the time that I had left it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was swarming with Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The front was very close to Busko.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
